message.body: Hope you feel better baby.
Feeling a little better. Didnt go to work so that helped. Still yucky tho. But...your Tiffany stuff came :)
Awww yay!!! I can put it store it someplace safe and then whip it out to show the chillens.
Haha thats what you want it for o.0??
....maybe.
What else would I want it for? I wanted to put it in our wedding album and show it off to the world!
Haha cutie. Its not so fancy. Just a few pieces of paper.
I don't care!!!!! Can you take a picture of it? I would like to know the specs of my ring :D
AND I DO WHAT I WANT!
Haha ok ok!!!! Crazy lady haha. Picture wont show everything. I can write it out if you like?
...you do what you want! Haha. I'm just picturing screaming I do what I want in my head and I'm laughing to myself.
...weirdo :-p...
:D weirdo you're spending the rest of your life with!!!!!
Hehe woohooo!!
Someone commented on my ring this morning. I was holding a starbucks cup and she said looked at me, nodded in the direction of my ring, and whispered "beautiful." Haha
Hahah ooo aint you fancy getting complements on your bling. It does look beautiful on you. Mmmhm
:D what can I say? I have a pretty good guy!
Naw just a really really lucky one!

Hehehe. Now give me what I want! Just take a picture. I don't need to see everything, I'm just curious. Not going to make me love me ring any less than I do. And lemme tell you, I'm pretty in love with it :D
Haha ok. Cant promise it'll be interesting. Phone camera is crap but here goes.
Hahah. I love you so much, you know that?
I hope you love me enough to let me refuse to send you a picture? It doesnt come out darling...seriously. Id have to go line by line. Youre gonna have to visit)
Oh that's okie. Of course I will visit! Yay!! Can I ask what the clarity of my ring is? I wanna know :)
Its a range. Says VS1, which is 5th highest bracket of 11, and means "very slightly included." Dunno. And color is the highest in the "near colorless" range
:D I figured the color was pretty colorless. I can't tell the clarity, but good to know. Thank you, my love!
Yeah, dunno what VS1 clarity really means. Sorry my love.
What the?! Don't be sorry! I don't really know what it means either. I just wanted to know so I could tell ppl who ask. Haha.
Thank you! But what do you have going on today? More NyQuil!
Haha okie dokie. They wont know either haha! But nah. Cant. Gotta go to work :-( Probably from 4pm until like...forever. Double shift
DOUBLE?! Por que?!
Well no one will do last nights junk. Theyre just gonna leave it for me
Boo I hate it.
Haha so do i
Hows today look for you?
Okay. I'm not going to my chem recitation because it's just a review and my prof said we didn't have to. I'm now doing some microbio and then I have lab at 230
Not too shabby :) Glad you dont have to go to chem and good luck with the micro! Get it outta the way!
O_O I forgot I ordered the hobbit and that it came out today! Should have been delivered!
